&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="mailto:lou@louplummer.lol?subject=500%20App%20Reviews%20Published!" style="text-decoration: underline;"&gt;✉️ 通过邮件回复&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 29 Mar 2026 10:30:00 +0000</pubDate></item></channel></rss>